{"tid":2152356,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"藝人課金撐新聞自由 陳潔玲掃清報攤《蘋果》 曾志豪專欄開天窗「向權貴堅定嘅抗議」","createTime":"2020-08-12T02:50:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T15:31:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"df1edf63ba9d1cd9ebc2a5ca693e06bde82c2b6a","tid":2152356,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T02:50:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200812/ZZYEZGSYRBBL3OZ73RX47HZU3M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200812%2FZZYEZGSYRBBL3OZ73RX47HZU3M%2F&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf3No2vAooDXMO4YLrfRUzdI%3D&h=842170a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200812%2FZZYEZGSYRBBL3OZ73RX47HZU3M%2F&h=abfb48d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200812/ZZYEZGSYRBBL3OZ73RX47HZU3M/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n藝人課金撐新聞自由 陳潔玲掃清報攤《蘋果》<br />\n曾志豪專欄開天窗「向權貴堅定嘅抗議」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港府前日以港版國安法，拘捕壹傳媒創辦人黎智英、他的兩位兒子及四名高層，並動用逾200名警員到《蘋果日報》大樓封鎖搜查。事件引起全港及國際關注，不少敢於發聲的藝人紛紛凌晨出街買《蘋果》及課金訂閱《蘋果》，兼在社交網貼相表態以示支持。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/cH482xQazSbYyAU6-LMxvil-OC0=/640x960/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SUIIT34PGNCDPJLDHU63P5DMOM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FcH482xQazSbYyAU6-LMxvil-OC0%3D%2F640x960%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSUIIT34PGNCDPJLDHU63P5DMOM.jpg&h=569a4e69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳潔玲 資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7L176Z0ES976BpStLhaKL4n8Bko=/720x960/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6DHARGZ3OFBEPGYNBJKO5K4OFY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7L176Z0ES976BpStLhaKL4n8Bko%3D%2F720x960%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6DHARGZ3OFBEPGYNBJKO5K4OFY.jpg&h=bdf2bd4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■陳潔玲昨日掃清報攤的《蘋果日報》，表示政府拘捕黎智英等令港人更加團結。 互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/F3k-2PK1cqut4u2Nw6UDhuYboTs=/720x960/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YO7FARWVKVHXPNPLSEZJDDCQ6M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FF3k-2PK1cqut4u2Nw6UDhuYboTs%3D%2F720x960%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYO7FARWVKVHXPNPLSEZJDDCQ6M.jpg&h=9278ffbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曾志豪。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/F3k-2PK1cqut4u2Nw6UDhuYboTs=/720x960/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YO7FARWVKVHXPNPLSEZJDDCQ6M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FF3k-2PK1cqut4u2Nw6UDhuYboTs%3D%2F720x960%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYO7FARWVKVHXPNPLSEZJDDCQ6M.jpg&h=9278ffbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■曾志豪昨早買了兩份《蘋果》，更在專欄中「開天窗」抗議。 互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n渣哥盡掃免費派發<br />\n<br />\n無綫前藝人陳潔玲昨晨天未光就掃光整檔報攤的《蘋果日報》，並於社交網留言：「開源道47號啲《蘋果》俾我掃晒。」網民大讚她「真女神」。她回覆時透露昨早特意清晨5時多在觀塘區報紙檔等送貨後，一口氣買了72份《蘋果日報》：「因為香港人唔可以冇咗《蘋果》，同埋我仲有買邊份報紙自由。《蘋果》不會因此倒下，政府咁做，反而令香港人更加團結。」<br />\n<br />\n曾志豪昨凌晨也開車到旺角買兩份報紙支持，他昨日在《蘋果》名為「下流準備」的專欄開天窗，只寫上「You can&rsquo;t kill us all」，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n譚小環老公渣哥昨早買了多份《蘋果》放在餐廳免費派發，並留言：「一早起身，經已盡力盡掃心中情。」而才女梁芷珊就加。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n柳俊江就貼手持幾份《蘋果》相，憶述與黎智英的「幾面之緣」，他說︰「。。。。。。。。。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/XRYfYmAq7IG4LZQzCjPLc9zjXa8=/720x960/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RD3PWJL5JZFDXBUT3EIMXU2FQI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXRYfYmAq7IG4LZQzCjPLc9zjXa8%3D%2F720x960%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRD3PWJL5JZFDXBUT3EIMXU2FQI.jpg&h=d7dfb7ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■譚小環的老公蔡強榮買了多份《蘋果》，放在餐廳內免費派發。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/F7jhI7g2Ei9rvpVRqqyB6rN7un0=/720x960/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LZPBGRZF3JHN5HBKIMA2Q5XFRE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FF7jhI7g2Ei9rvpVRqqyB6rN7un0%3D%2F720x960%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLZPBGRZF3JHN5HBKIMA2Q5XFRE.jpg&h=9346af1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n譚小環、蔡強榮 資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n韻詩買股票抗爭<br />\n<br />\n何韻詩昨日凌晨開始轉貼《蘋果》直播出版印冊過程，其後她又貼相指自己買了五份報紙，也買了壹傳媒股票，她回覆時說︰「買幾多唔係重點，係好黐線好唔理性㗎，但相比令人發狂嘅環境，呢個已經最合情合理合法嘅抗爭。」<br />\n<br />\n黃耀明昨早亦貼手執《蘋果》相片，並留言：「臨瞓前走咗落街買兩份，如果唔係我會瞓唔着。」藍奕邦則在網上聲援：「。。。。。。。。」而阮民安也到便利店買報紙：「。。。。。。。。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RlvXMy9QvDTzBsdvCxUi9c5Z7ys=/960x720/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XQVGTM55AFAP7GYFF5M6D7EQ3M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRlvXMy9QvDTzBsdvCxUi9c5Z7ys%3D%2F960x720%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXQVGTM55AFAP7GYFF5M6D7EQ3M.jpg&h=a83e6d29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■何韻詩由前日已經留意《蘋果》的新聞，昨日買了五份《蘋果》作支持。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7a_heOhA3zwree5W9F7CYJQuvkQ=/640x960/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OZ44XJVJHFF2VOX7ULCYFRM5ZE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7a_heOhA3zwree5W9F7CYJQuvkQ%3D%2F640x960%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOZ44XJVJHFF2VOX7ULCYFRM5ZE.jpg&h=6cc2e19f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■柳俊江（右）憶起與黎智英見面的往事，指對方是個浪漫主義者。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bhxQV9OGRmcwUHa9Bn4XiAlcQbg=/720x960/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WLCX7AVZARCEREFYVBPOWFV7AA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbhxQV9OGRmcwUHa9Bn4XiAlcQbg%3D%2F720x960%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWLCX7AVZARCEREFYVBPOWFV7AA.jpg&h=9c23aa95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■黃耀明表示昨日要買到《蘋果日報》才可以安心入睡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/D4cIvsVkioyNUA-lrWLu2o-Qv_o=/720x960/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EVXHUF4DHFCJHD6JSSLSZQSUUU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FD4cIvsVkioyNUA-lrWLu2o-Qv_o%3D%2F720x960%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEVXHUF4DHFCJHD6JSSLSZQSUUU.jpg&h=7992fa31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■藍奕邦在網上留言聲援支持新聞自由的人士。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/t4ciJle471LldPO_ZLiqBvTBqSI=/720x960/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KIQ7CFF7HZEZFPUQ5CXYNKJ5BA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ft4ciJle471LldPO_ZLiqBvTBqSI%3D%2F720x960%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKIQ7CFF7HZEZFPUQ5CXYNKJ5BA.jpg&h=494cd81d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■梁芷珊已登記成為《蘋果》VIP。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/GhefnhntreLyrtVg5aEEYyWrIZ8=/720x960/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VEOK6PU7GVFM3HO4PTAPJZVV7U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FGhefnhntreLyrtVg5aEEYyWrIZ8%3D%2F720x960%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVEOK6PU7GVFM3HO4PTAPJZVV7U.jpg&h=c59cf063&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■阮民安呼籲市民以行動支持新聞自由。"},{"pid":"8b1362a68a9c75e5ed8f765bad912227038be1ca","tid":2152356,"uid":158735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T02:51:28.000Z","msg":"有個辦法可以幫蘋果日報增加銷量<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2152309\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2152309</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a69b6efda1da0c11c0ea148d222800a6cc916e91","tid":2152356,"uid":144079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T02:52:53.000Z","msg":"渣哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f946c3d0a8da87b2d1d16b664c62e5ba8105b8e1","tid":2152356,"uid":9327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T03:12:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9452947a8bf09be17de446d45f6043157adcf662","tid":2152356,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T15:31:19.000Z","msg":"Sonia Ng提供PayCode：「既然撐蘋果，撐埋我啦！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2153589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2153589</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}